<!--<h4><hi rend="italic">North Face.</hi></h4>-->

<p>
<lb n="1"/>śākhābdē ni<unclear>dhi</unclear>khēṁdugaṇitē grastē ravau rāhuṇā śrī
<lb n="2" break="no"/>matsiṁhagirīśvarāya harayē lōkaikabhartrē sudhī<supplied reason="omitted">r</supplied>nā
<lb n="3" break="no"/>nāpuṣpavirājitāṁ samakarōtsatpuṣpavāṭī<supplied reason="omitted">ṁ</supplied> śubhāmā
<lb n="4" break="no"/>caṁdrārkkamanūnadharmmanilaya<supplied reason="omitted">ḥ</supplied> śrīpōmiseṭṭi prabhuḥ <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g>
<lb n="5"/>svasti <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> śrīmattribhuvanacakravartti kulōttuṁgacōḍadēva
<lb n="6" break="no"/>ra pravarddhamāna vijayarājyasaṁvatsaraṁbulu
<lb n="7"/>11 ṇḍagu srā<supplied reason="omitted">hi</supplied> viṣusaṁkrāṁttinimittamuna jīyyaha
<lb n="8" break="no"/>ri śrīnara(si)siṁhadēvaraku penuṁgoṇḍa mmulakola
<lb n="9"/>prōliseṭṭi koḍku pōmiseṭṭi puṣpavanamunakuṁ beṭṭina mā
<lb n="10" break="no"/>ḍalu padiyā<unclear>ru</unclear> mrucciṁcillaṁ ddana groppiṁccina ceṟvutūrppu
<lb n="11"/>kommuna beṭṭi groppiṁcci yī ceṟvukriṁdda bhūmi viṟci śrībhaṇḍā
<lb n="12" break="no"/>ramunakuṁ gōru veṭṭaṁgalayadi yī tirunaṁddavanamu ceyya śrī 
<lb n="13" break="no"/>dharuce<unclear>lva</unclear>ku śrīnārasiṁhatūmu tūmeṇḍu prāla tirupa
<lb n="14" break="no"/>riyalamu niruvadi cinnamuluṁ beṭṭaṁgalavāru Ī dha
<lb n="15" break="no"/>rmmāna kahitaṁ talaṁcchināru gaṁggakaṟta vē gōlalaṁ boḍci
<lb n="16" break="no"/>na dhōṣamunaṁ bōduru Ī dharmma śrīvaiṣṇava rakṣa [<g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g>]
</p>

